dct_title_s: Korea city plans 1:12,500. Kyongsong south. A.M.S. L952
dct_description_sm: AMS (FEC) Alternate title: Kyonsong, Korea: Kyonggi-do. In upper left margin: "Korea city plans 1:12,500". Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. Korean names transcribed according to the McCune-Reishauer system, Japanese form of Korean names (shown in parentheses) transcribed according to the modified Hepburn (Romaji) System.
